 Marissa Mayer
(II)


 
Miscellaneous Crew





Marissa Mayer was born on May 30, 1975 in Wausau, Wisconsin, USA as Marissa Ann Mayer. She is known for her work on Inside the Mind of Google (2009), Miss Representation (2011) and Davos 2014: The Global Agenda (2014). She has been married to Zachary Bogue since December 12, 2009. They have three children.            
See full bio »
            
 


